  Boston events: a brief mention and the date of more than 5,000 events that transpired in Boston from 1630 to 1880, covering a period of 250 years, together with other occurrences of interest, arranged in alphabetical order Edward H. Savage, author of Police Recollections; Or Boston by Daylight and Gas-Light. Tufts University  &Perseus.publish;  

